{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Runehaven is an atmospheric first-person roguelike dungeon crawler. Explore eerie, procedurally generated dungeons, battle vile creatures, solve puzzles, discover hidden secrets, and dodge deadly traps in your quest for survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/extras/runic_magic_header.png?t=1737752927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/extras/runic_magic.gif?t=1737752927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft spells by combining different runes using a magic system inspired by Ultima and Arx Fatalis! Each rune affects the spell in an unique and emergent way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/extras/voxel_physics_header.png?t=1737752927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/extras/voxel_physics_3.gif?t=1737752927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a fully destructible voxel environment. Nearly everything in the game can be destroyed, either by the player or the enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> An emergent runic magic system.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Voxel physics with a fully destructible voxel environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully procedural dungeons where every map layout is unique.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose between various melee, ranged and magic weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dual wielding.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge deadly traps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Voxel graphics with physically based rendering.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore unique biomes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Permanent death.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Solve various puzzles. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fight against different monsters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Discover secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Level up your character. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Modding support.  </p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737752927","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/page.bg.jpg?t=1737752927","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/54c519940bd1dd0e75b506706ef4e66b247fe4a2/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737752927","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/54c519940bd1dd0e75b506706ef4e66b247fe4a2/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737752927","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2918260,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Runehaven is an atmospheric first-person roguelike dungeon crawler. Explore eerie, procedurally generated dungeons, battle vile creatures, solve puzzles, discover hidden secrets, and dodge deadly traps in your quest for survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/extras/runic_magic_header.png?t=1737752927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/extras/runic_magic.gif?t=1737752927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft spells by combining different runes using a magic system inspired by Ultima and Arx Fatalis! Each rune affects the spell in an unique and emergent way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/extras/voxel_physics_header.png?t=1737752927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/extras/voxel_physics_3.gif?t=1737752927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a fully destructible voxel environment. Nearly everything in the game can be destroyed, either by the player or the enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> An emergent runic magic system.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Voxel physics with a fully destructible voxel environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully procedural dungeons where every map layout is unique.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose between various melee, ranged and magic weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dual wielding.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge deadly traps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Voxel graphics with physically based rendering.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore unique biomes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Permanent death.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Solve various puzzles. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fight against different monsters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Discover secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Level up your character. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Modding support.  </p></li></ul>","developers":["Cikoria Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676030/header.jpg?t=1737752927","i